Class Word

  • java.lang.Object
    • Word
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeComparable

    public class Word
extends java.lang.Object
implements TreeComparable
    The Word class defines a Word object. A Word object may be constructed given a String and LinePosition, a String word, or no parameters.
    Version:
    5/17/2019
    Author:
    Joshua Matson
